comments.content:
It must be **[Britannic Bold](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018141828/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=URW&ffam=Britannic%20Bold%20-%20Bold&fid=e1ad73effcc9084cf43cd1c06040829b&fsize=60&text=ROUTE%20INFO&wrap=2)**, Stephenson Blake (1901) available from Linotype & URW++

------------------  
I found it using "Find my Font": [http://www.findmyfont.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018141828/http:/www.findmyfont.com/ "http://www.findmyfont.com")
